      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Ahmad Bin Muhammad, from Muhammad Bin Ismail, from Mansour Bin Yunus, from Al Arzamy, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘The springs burst out from underneath the Kabah’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "1. A number of our people have narrated from Ahmad ibn Muhammad from Muhammad ibn ’Isma‘il from Mansur ibn Yunus from al-‘ Arzamiy who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘The fountains gushed from under the al-Ka‘bah.’” "
        ]
      }
